title: Spotmau PowerSuite 2009 Professional * BOOTABLE ISO
description:
Spotmau PowerSuite 2009 offers you a complete solution to all
your computer problems in an easy way! It is an everyday
toolset for PC maintenance and optimization, and also an
emergency kit for rescuing and recovering your precious
data and system when Windows crashes.

With Spotmau Powersuite 2009, you can:

* Boot up any computer
* Speed up your Windows
* Find out any password
* Recover data from deleted, crashed, or formatted hard disk
* Repair Windows problems
* Clone your system & data
* Protect your computer privacy

Boot Up Windows 98/ME/2K/2003/XP/NT/Vista
